    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like a reconnection though. it feels like a dead end. like i'm standing at a terminal and all the flights have already departed. i'm just... tired of the journey. i feel like i've completed my itinerary and there's nothing left on the schedule but the end of the line.",
